ios.subtitle: A place to start musical ideas

editorialNotes.standard: We never expected a lilypad to unlock our musical abilities. Yet here we are, somehow carving beautiful melodies from a selection of them. Lily isnt entirely whimsical, however: its lilies are essentially deft musical instruments providing organic lessons in scales, harmonies, and tempo. Be sure to save and upload your compositions, too.
editorialNotes.short: Who expected a lily pad to unlock your musical abilities?
